                            <comment id="272456" author="spiechurski" created="Wed, 10 Jun 2020 13:35:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have been wrong all the way with this ....&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Failed while submitting the ticket, did not look properly at the source code I was watching, and did not look the proper version of the source code (b2_12 instead of master).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="272453" author="degremoa" created="Wed, 10 Jun 2020 13:24:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Actually flock is the default since 2.13: &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/32091/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/32091/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10885&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10885&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="272443" author="spiechurski" created="Wed, 10 Jun 2020 10:22:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry, this is conditional to compile-time option ENABLE_FLOCK, which I thought was enabled by default.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This ticket has no reason to exist.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Please close.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="272442" author="spiechurski" created="Wed, 10 Jun 2020 09:46:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The documentation section 44.14.3 for the flock / localflock / noflock mount options says that the default option is noflock.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, looking at the code, it seems to me that the default is &quot;flock&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
